    "## 9. Pipeline Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "| Layer | Technology | Source 1 (GitHub) | Source 2 (Weather) |\n",
    "|---|---|---|---|\n",
    "| **Source** | REST API | GitHub Search API | Open-Meteo Historical |\n",
    "| **Transport** | Kafka | `batch-github-repos` | `batch-weather-history` |\n",
    "| **Process** | PySpark Batch | Stars, forks, score | Temp range, rain flag |\n",
    "| **Staging** | PostgreSQL | `github_repositories` | `historical_weather` |\n",
    "| **Warehouse** | Amazon Redshift | via S3 COPY | via S3 COPY |\n",
    "| **Schedule** | Airflow DAG | Daily 02:00 WIB | Daily 01:00 WIB |\n",
    "\n",
    "**Data Volume:**  \n",
    "- GitHub: ~150 repos/day × 5 languages = ~750 records  \n",
    "- Weather: 5 cities × 90 days = 450 historical records per run\n",
    "\n",
    "**SLA:** Complete pipeline run < 15 minutes per day"
